{"tid":1360776,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"會自組小隊夢遊嘅兄弟/ 自衛隊/ 急救隊, 有冇考慮可以建立一個通用嘅編制","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T21:19:53.000Z","uid":16879,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4d38913508b40982a2da76e20e7706166a812bae","tid":1360776,"uid":16879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"小弟愚見，有編制嘅存在會對小隊好有幫助<br />\n<br />\n好處:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1. 釐清從屬或權責關係</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係叫你起大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係叫你大石砸死蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n而係當你遇上另外一隊自組小隊果時<br />\n<br />\n有編制的話，可以快速有效咁同對方溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且可以有效管理小隊內部，避免內哄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2. 容易指揮調動及整合</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n當混亂情況時，有個小隊入邊大家都認同嘅人可以快速咁協調同整合隊員嘅意見<br />\n(例如進定退? 幾時退?)<br />\n<br />\n而且當有需要時，編制同性質相近嘅小隊可以快速咁Plug and Play即插即用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如香港保衛戰時：「大陸旅」退守港島之後可以快速咁整合入去「港島旅」，再劃分做「西旅」和「東旅」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 容易估算人手同物資，減輕物資站負擔</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果大家都用相近嘅編制，可以快速估計到可動用or需要嘅人手同物資有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自組小隊帶得夠物資的話，有助減輕物資站負擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4.顯出班狗幾冇紀律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟整理咗維基上邊嘅資料(各國編制同埋香港1972年前的警階):<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8mLRHLH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8mLRHLH.jpg&h=dee6a4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個編制係小隊內部存在就ok，唔洗同全世界講<br />\n唔洗特登去俾人知<br />\n唔知大家點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b936ccb616ad4371d749556a21b73cae5807a78","tid":1360776,"uid":16879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:23:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a799105304891637509ff0b878d033e101c1a212","tid":1360776,"uid":16879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:24:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"680a413641e36e941f8c4ac0681146b63630c319","tid":1360776,"uid":16879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa4e027dbc0d025c621b958f112fead09a5a3eb4","tid":1360776,"uid":16879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"041ca4efdf0b1ec2b72f257afeefbce69add3403","tid":1360776,"uid":16879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:25:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"60124f8752d5063bc5c44e34e3d6ea7f37c17b6c","tid":1360776,"uid":16879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9a997536feb0be70e9fb67fbf4acc3abdb07cd5e","tid":1360776,"uid":16879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s